Quick Example ‚Äã

javascript
// Initialize Siraaj Analytics
const analytics = new Analytics({
  apiUrl: 'http://localhost:8080',
  projectId: 'my-website',
  autoTrack: true
});

// Track custom events
analytics.track('button_clicked', {
  button_id: 'signup',
  location: 'hero'
});

// Identify users
analytics.identify('user-123', {
  email: 'user@example.com',
  plan: 'premium'
});

Why Siraaj? ‚Äã

Siraaj is built for developers who need a fast, privacy-focused, and self-hosted analytics solution. Unlike traditional analytics platforms:

  • ‚úÖ No external dependencies - All data stays on your server
